Namespace Goedel.Places PalimpsestConstants
	|Constants specified in hallambaker-mesh-schema

File CatalogLabels
	Enum CookieType "Cookie labels"
		Code Session "Authentication session cookie"
			Description
				|Authentication session cookie
		Code Temporary "Temporary authentication session cookie"
			Description
				|Temporary authentication session cookie


	Enum StoreType "Store labels"

		Code Places "Places catalog"
			Description
				|One catalog per forum, index for everything
			Description
				|Filename: Place.dcat

		Code Members "Members catalog"
			Description
				|One catalog per forum, maps external users to a forum identifier
			Description
				|Filename: Member.dcat


