File Configuration
	Enum Limit "Limits"
		Flag RequestSize	1 "Request size in bytes"
		Flag PostsPerHour	2 "Posts per hour"
		Flag PostSize		3 "Post size in bytes"
		Flag CommentSize	4 "Comment size in characters"
		Flag UserStorage	5 "User storage in bytes"

	Enum Privilege "Privileges"
		Flag CreatePlace		 1 "Create new places"
		Flag CreateFeed			 2 "Create new feed"
		Flag CreatePost			 3 "Create post"
		Flag CreateComment		 4 "Create comment"

		Flag ReadPlace			 5 "Create new places"
		Flag ReedFeed			 6 "Create new feed"
		Flag ReadPost			 7 "Create post"
		Flag ReadComment		 8 "Create comment"

		Flag DeletePlace		 9 "Delete feed"
		Flag DeleteFeed			10 "Delete feed"
		Flag DeletePost			11 "Delete post"
		Flag DeleteComment		12 "Delete comment"

		Flag GrantAdministrator	16 "Create new places"
		Flag GrantModerator		17 "Create new places"
		Flag GrantAuthor		18 "Create new places"
		Flag GrantCommentator	19 "Create new places"

		Flag Suspend			20 "Suspend member"
		Flag Ban				21 "Ban member"
		Flag Status				22 "Set member status"